PKPD model for clearance of caffeine

Description

This model is a physiological-base pharmacokinetic model (PBPK) for the absorption, distribution, metabolism and elimination of caffeine encoded in SBML.

The content of this model has been carefully created in a manual research effort.
This file has been created by Matthias Koenig.
